name: Mustang GT
description: So the Mustang is a sports car with very few flaws of one. Sure it is not perfect, but with that price tag, you get a lot of American muscle for your money. The Mustang has a rich heritage, is an icon and more importantly in the latest generation is an accomplished car too.
